      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "text": "1. Nodes form signing groups\n2. TSS ceremony: each node\n   gets a key SHARE\n3. Raw key NEVER exists\n4. 18 signers per ceremony\n5. Rotate every 3 days\n6. Signers combine shares\n   to produce valid signature",
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "1. Nodes form signing groups\n2. TSS ceremony: each node\n   gets a key SHARE\n3. Raw key NEVER exists\n4. 18 signers per ceremony\n5. Rotate every 3 days\n6. Signers combine shares\n   to produce valid signature",
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
