      "originalText": "1. Attacker funds since April\n2. Spends ~$300K to become\n   a Thorchain node validator\n3. Gets into signer group\n4. Next day: somehow has\n   the RAW PRIVATE KEY\n5. Key should not exist!\n6. Drains $10M vault",
